These examples demonstrate how to utilize the Patherizer Route Optimization API. The Patherizer API is a cross browser REST service, that is multi stop route optimization software, to be used by multiple calls to calculate and optimize routes for multiple vehicles. The API currently supports a maximum of 100 stops per route or request, including the start destination and the end destination. Implementation source code samples are available in VB.NET, VBA, C#, PHP, Java, Android, iOS, Python, Ruby and NodeJS.
